(41, 6, 2, 41, 1, 21, 22, NULL, 'Authority in Teaching', 'Both passages emphasize the astonishment of the listeners at Jesus'' teaching. In Mark 6:2, they marvel at his wisdom and mighty works, while in Mark 1:22, they are amazed at his authoritative doctrine.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
