(41, 6, 3, 41, 15, 40, 40, NULL, 'Family Connections in Mark', 'This connection highlights the mention of Mary, the mother of James and Joses, in both passages. Both verses emphasize familial ties, linking Jesus'' earthly family to the women present at his crucifixion.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
